---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-50 pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-gray-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-12">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
        <img 
          src="https://ccic.cat/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/logo-ccic.png" 
          alt="CCIC Logo" 
          class="h-14 w-fit opacity-80 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition"
        />
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Transformem el sector cap a una construcció més eficient, sostenible i preparada per al futur.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-bold uppercase text-sm mb-6 tracking-widest">Més informació</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-bold mr-2">Telèfon:</span> 
            <a href="tel:+34626931144" class="hover:text-blue-600">+34 626 931 144</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-bold mr-2">Email:</span> 
            <a href="mailto:cluster@ccic.cat" class="hover:text-blue-600">cluster@ccic.cat</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start leading-snug">
            <span class="font-bold mr-2">Direcció:</span> 
            Cami del Riu s/n, Molí Fariner, 08760 Martorell, Catalunya.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-gray-900 font-bold uppercase text-sm mb-6 tracking-widest">Eixos estratègics</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600">Co-share</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600">Co-mentor</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600">Co-factory</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-400">
      <div class="flex space-x-4 mb-4 md:mb-0">
        <a href="#" class="hover:underline text-gray-500">Politica de privacitat</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:underline text-gray-500">Política de cookies</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:underline text-gray-500">Avís legal</a>
      </div>
      <p>
        © {currentYear} CCIC. Desenvolupada per: <span class="font-semibold italic text-gray-500">Destino Bahamas</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>